body:
There are 3 layers of Minecraft
They are called the Surface, The Middle, and the Dark.

Now, Minecraft is a place meant for Children, the Average Minecraft player visits the "Surface".


What is the surface?
The surface are things that are things normal to Minecraft, Like minecraftforums or avicus.net. 
Things like Forge Mods and others, Pretty much like Google, Servers that are not meant for harm but for fun, like Avicus or Mineplex and all that other jazz. Texture Packs too. OBVIOUSLY HACK CLIENTS 2 EVERY LITTLE KID USES EM

But, there is somewhere quite deep along that surface, Its called The Middle


What is the Middle? 
The Middle is very different from the Surface, Far different, its mostly made up of things that are against EULA and usually include things that are malicious or harmful to the Minecraft Community. 
The things you will find in The Middle are things like  Minecraft name Snipers,  Minecraft Server Bots. Alt generators
and "Free optifine cape websites". If these things arent bad enough, the Dark is much more different.

But If you adventure deep enough, you will find something very dangerous and are just outright ILLEGAL 





What is... THE DARK.
Now, this is dangerous, This is on a whole different level. Almost all these things are illegal and just outright wrong,
What in the Dark is illegal,

The things YOU will find in the Dark, are Minecraft Account Crackers, servers for Pedos, servers that are offensive to other players, Like NaziCraft or SexyCraft,(Mojang blacklisted or removed most of these but they still lurk around somewhere). You will find Minecraft NSFW Content( yeah, **** pretty much)  Plugin Leaks, Paid Clients, Minecraft Server DDOS Programs, And a whole lot more, al


Anyways, thats all for dis p0st, there is a Deep Web in Minecraft, trust me there is. 

Anyways, Thats all for now,




~Clickn huehuehue
